{
  "texts": [
    "This ensures that the recommendations not only become more aligned with user preferences but also adapt to evolving travel trends and emergent destinations or experiences.",
    "The system is designed to foster continuous user engagement by: Sending Periodic Updates: About new destinations, activities, or changes that might align with their past preferences and feedback.",
    "Requesting Ongoing Feedback: Even during the trip, to make real-time adjustments to the itinerary where possible.",
    "Personalized Alerts: Sending alerts for deals, news, or information that is specifically tailored to individual user preferences.",
    "User profiles within the system are dynamic, evolving entities."
  ]
}